<view class="product-page">
  <image class="page-bg" src="{{heroBackground}}" mode="aspectFill" />
  <view class="page-shade"></view>
  <view class="nav"><view class="back" bindtap="goBack">‹</view><text>机构训赛经营增长平台</text><view></view></view>
  <scroll-view class="page-scroll" scroll-y enhanced show-scrollbar="{{false}}">
    <view class="hero">
      <image class="brand-logo" src="{{logo}}" mode="aspectFit" />
      <view class="hero-badge"><text>赛小蜂篮球 · 机构版</text><text>GROWTH</text></view>
      <text class="hero-kicker">TRAIN · GAME · GROWTH</text>
      <view class="hero-title"><text>让训练与比赛</text><text class="hero-title-accent">持续转化为增长</text></view>
      <text class="hero-desc">让每一次训练与比赛，持续转化为家长认可、续费行动与机构增长。</text>
      <view class="hero-points"><text>训赛一体化</text><text>家长价值</text><text>经营增长</text></view>
    </view>

    <view class="content">
      <view class="position-card">
        <view class="position-mark">核心差异</view>
        <text class="position-title">不是增加一套管理工具，而是建立一条增长链路</text>
        <text class="position-desc">平台不替代机构运营，但让关键经营动作更早发生、更容易执行。数据不只说明发生了什么，还要推动下一步行动。</text>
      </view>

      <view class="section-head"><view><text class="section-kicker">增长链路</text><text class="section-title">训赛数据不会停在报表里</text></view><text class="section-no">01</text></view>
      <view class="growth-chain">
        <view class="growth-card" wx:for="{{growthChain}}" wx:key="order">
          <view class="growth-card-head"><text class="growth-order">{{item.order}}</text><text class="growth-title">{{item.title}}</text></view>
          <text class="growth-desc">{{item.desc}}</text>
          <text class="growth-result">{{item.result}}</text>
        </view>
      </view>

      <view class="role-panel">
        <view class="section-head"><view><text class="section-kicker">角色与权限</text><text class="section-title">同一套产品语言，每个人只看自己的工作</text></view><text class="section-no">02</text></view>
        <view class="role-row" wx:for="{{roles}}" wx:key="label">
          <view class="role-label">{{item.label}}</view>
          <view class="role-copy"><text class="role-title">{{item.title}}</text><text class="role-desc">{{item.desc}}</text></view>
        </view>
      </view>

      <view class="task-panel">
        <view class="section-head"><view><text class="section-kicker">增长任务</text><text class="section-title">不只给一张报表，更给一份可执行清单</text></view><text class="section-no">03</text></view>
        <text class="task-intro">异常数据转成带负责人、时限、处理过程和结果的任务。</text>
        <view class="task-steps">
          <view class="task-step" wx:for="{{taskSteps}}" wx:key="order"><text class="task-order">{{item.order}}</text><text class="task-title">{{item.title}}</text><text class="task-desc">{{item.desc}}</text></view>
        </view>
      </view>

      <view class="section-head"><view><text class="section-kicker">训赛壁垒</text><text class="section-title">比赛不是附加功能，而是独有的增长场景</text></view><text class="section-no">04</text></view>
      <text class="proof-lead">训练创造能力，比赛证明能力，内容放大价值。</text>
      <view class="proof-list"><view class="proof-card" wx:for="{{proofPoints}}" wx:key="title"><view class="proof-dot"></view><view><text class="proof-title">{{item.title}}</text><text class="proof-desc">{{item.desc}}</text></view></view></view>

      <view class="pilot-card">
        <view class="pilot-top"><view><text class="pilot-eyebrow">{{accessEyebrow}}</text><text class="pilot-title">{{accessTitle}}</text></view><text class="pilot-mark">PILOT</text></view>
        <view class="pilot-path"><text>01 选定指标</text><text>02 跑通闭环</text><text>03 验证结果</text></view>
        <view class="pilot-note">{{accessNote}}</view>
      </view>
      <view class="safe-space"></view>
    </view>
  </scroll-view>
  <view class="footer"><view><text>机构训赛经营增长平台</text><text>一个校区 · 一个指标 · 一个闭环</text></view><button class="pilot-button" open-type="contact" show-message-card="{{true}}" send-message-title="咨询赛小蜂机构训赛经营增长平台" send-message-path="/pages/education-product/index" bindtap="recordPilotLead">{{accessButtonLabel}}</button></view>
</view>
